description:
&lt;p&gt;Senior Nutrition Support Dietitian&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have an exciting opportunity for x2 Band 6 Dietitians (fixed-term) to join our Nutrition Support Team. We are looking for enthusiastic, self-motivated individuals who have experience in managing malnutrition in the community and with a good knowledge of the adult appropriate Oral Nutritional Supplement (ONS) prescribing initiative. You will be responsible for your own caseload whereby patients may require virtual/F2F clinics, home and nursing home visits as the service requires. The role supports patients at risk of malnutrition, adopting a Food First approach where possible and the appropriate use of Oral Nutritional Supplements as well as training of healthcare professionals. You will be providing a Nutrition Support Dietetic Service in the boroughs of Hammersmith and Fulham, Kensington and Chelsea and Westminster; however you will also work closely with all Nutrition Support Dietitians throughout CLCH.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be responsible for:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your own caseload of patients who require oral nutrition support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting the Oral Nutritional Supplement prescribing initiative&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Training of healthcare professionals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews are scheduled for&lt;strong&gt; 19th November 2020&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
